); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Tea and coffee will be available, alongside some musical entertainment, in the foyer from 9.00am.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The event itself will start at 9:30am and&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">will be finished by 11:00am.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Speech Day is our final event of the academic year and we kindly ask that all children and parents attend. It is going to be a fantastic morning to celebrate another great year. Children will perform, and prizes will be awarded.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This year, to create a more family friendly atmosphere, we ask that parents and carers <b>bring their children directly to the event</b>. Families and friends will sit together for the event so that parents can join in on the celebrations.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">There is no school on this day. Parents will be responsible for their childrenâ€™s supervision during the event. School uniform, with blazers and black shoes, is the expected attire for the children.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Early Years children finish school at 11:30am on Thursday 21st June. However, you are welcome to bring your Nursery or Reception children along with you to this Speech Day event, if you wish to do so.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Should you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Regards,</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mr Adam Johnson</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Principal</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style=""><font style=""><br></font></div></font></span><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style=""><i style=""><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600" style="" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b style="">World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font></div></div>]]></td>
